{"tid":1324863,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB同其他紅媒根本係蜘蛛俠果間號角日報","createTime":"2019-07-16T16:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T08:24:30.000Z","uid":165336,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"20f2ad4b0e6f7f6658a52d3afed303191948548e","tid":1324863,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:34:25.000Z","msg":"邊一代既蜘蛛俠，包括埋Game版既蜘蛛俠<br />\n都會見到有間叫號角日報既野<br />\n個老闆極度憎蜘蛛俠，專門抹黑佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記憶中當年八爪魚博士打劫銀行<br />\n蜘蛛俠咁辛苦救完人<br />\n呢間仆街野居然寫蜘蛛俠打劫銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且成日話佢阻住警察人做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想講既係，蜘蛛俠最大既敵人唔係任何強大既奸角<br />\n而係呢間撚屌野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢間野陷蜘蛛俠於不義<br />\n害埋佢全家，搞到佢救人都綁手綁腳<br />\n又得唔到民眾支持<br />\n明明係英雄俾佢講到變左暴徒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n居民睇到乜就信乜<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">甚至將壞人造成既破壞都歸咎於英雄</span></span></strong><br />\n香港人唔好咁撚蠢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e340b31e2fe3f487ab7f24987b8fc2ba1dce806f","tid":1324863,"uid":165336,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:58:56.000Z","msg":"我講漏左一樣野<br />\n號角日報係最大敵人既原因<br />\n係因為無論你有幾多人<br />\n有幾好打都好<br />\n你係唔可以對佢做任何野唔可以打鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正如我地全香港咁多人憎TVB都搞唔到佢一樣<br />\n佢可以做任何野對付你<br />\n但我地唔可以做任何野對付佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩抵制果d根本R痕<br />\n亞視都頂到咁多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e5561bf14fac58d861e3238ae48e4a850d559d7","tid":1324863,"uid":48791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T19:13:42.000Z","msg":"呢排睇完far from home就玩返隻game個DLC<br />\n<br />\n同樓主想法一樣<br />\n<br />\nJJJ一聽到聽眾讚spiderman就cut人線 好撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"321d47f8ca78e75de912d40d6ff44c7818b1d8e6","tid":1324863,"uid":260256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e5561bf14fac58d861e3238ae48e4a850d559d7","tid":1324863,"uid":48791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T19:13:42.000Z","msg":"呢排睇完far from home就玩返隻game個DLC<br />\n<br />\n同樓主想法一樣<br />\n<br />\nJJJ一聽到聽眾讚spiderman就cut人線 好撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T20:02:38.000Z","msg":"(收咪) sor...借過...當我哋今日冇採訪過..."},{"pid":"82006ecfb51cdf6bbd897b1e6e58bf637fbd216e","tid":1324863,"uid":196445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T20:25:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d8113d27f8be2b480c27bc588b416814c8b60f","tid":1324863,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:33:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25f8b01311ad5dd11aecd9d524cd3013447577e","tid":1324863,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8e5561bf14fac58d861e3238ae48e4a850d559d7","tid":1324863,"uid":48791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T19:13:42.000Z","msg":"呢排睇完far from home就玩返隻game個DLC<br />\n<br />\n同樓主想法一樣<br />\n<br />\nJJJ一聽到聽眾讚spiderman就cut人線 好撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:46:00.000Z","msg":"你睇埋最新果套戲仲嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd1c7b6c4d9bb0770749eb7cffdc5b44714af70d"